1
00:00:04,864 --> 00:00:08,425
I heard that Graham's comet
will soon be visible!

2
00:00:08,638 --> 00:00:10,435
What's that?

3
00:00:10,643 --> 00:00:13,510
I know Halley's comet,
but not this one.

4
00:00:13,716 --> 00:00:18,483
It's the comet that passes
close to Earth every 50 years.

5
00:00:19,329 --> 00:00:20,489
Wow.

6
00:00:20,699 --> 00:00:24,965
I'm sure it's this Thursday
when it'll pass by Earth again.

7
00:00:25,610 --> 00:00:28,670
How wonderful!
This Thursday, you say?

8
00:00:28,884 --> 00:00:31,910
How romantic!

9
00:00:34,596 --> 00:00:39,966
But you can't see it with the naked
eye. You have to go to an observatory.

10
00:00:40,176 --> 00:00:44,840
What would happen
if a comet crashed into Earth?

11
00:00:45,053 --> 00:00:47,578
I guess we'd all be blown to bits.

12
00:00:47,792 --> 00:00:52,388
-Then what will you do, Ryoko?
-Get my important things and run!

13
00:00:52,603 --> 00:00:54,969
-To where?
-Your important things?

14
00:00:55,175 --> 00:00:58,702
-Let me think...
-Important things, she says.

15
00:00:58,917 --> 00:01:02,717
-My parents, for sure!
-Mine's my favorite fishing pole.

16
00:01:02,926 --> 00:01:07,295
My pillow! I can't sleep without it!

17
00:01:10,376 --> 00:01:15,780
-You guys are a lost cause.
-What about you, Sawatari?

18
00:01:16,991 --> 00:01:20,222
Let's run to the end of the world!

19
00:01:24,307 --> 00:01:27,640
No way.

20
00:01:28,416 --> 00:01:33,649
A COMET APPROACHES!
THE EARTH'S FINAL NIGHT??

21
00:01:34,062 --> 00:01:35,552
You're all idiots!

22
00:01:35,766 --> 00:01:40,669
A comet never leaves its orbit,
so it'll never crash into Earth.

23
00:01:40,877 --> 00:01:44,574
I said "suppose"!
Don't call me an idiot, you idiot!

24
00:01:44,786 --> 00:01:46,720
You want a fight?

25
00:01:46,924 --> 00:01:52,328
So that's it! You don't have anything
important to take, so you're mad.

26
00:01:52,604 --> 00:01:56,563
What? You're wrong!
I do too have something precious!

27
00:01:57,146 --> 00:01:59,979
-Then tell us!
-You really want to know?

28
00:02:00,187 --> 00:02:05,022
Are you two friends or enemies?
Make up your mind!

29
00:02:09,742 --> 00:02:13,735
-Who wants to be friends with him?
-Same here!

30
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:21,074
Advertise your product or brand here
